storyInfo: A plain and simple day in the life of Ceobe.

attributes.content: When was the last time you performed maintenance on your equipment?
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: It's about time. You’d better get to work on them.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: You still have that maintenance diagram I drew for you?
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Yup! I hung it up in my room.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Are there sufficient tools and consumables in that room? If you've run out, you can take some now.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Let’s clean up and pack up. Then we can head out when the fire dies down.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Yes, I have to go check on the boiler room, then collect the materials I ordered from the warehouse  . Don't have time to worry about the fire.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: That's not a good job   for you.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: You have things you need to do as well, right?
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: I made you a lunch, remember to take it when you leave.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: I'll come find you when I finish.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: I'll go to my room to take care of my babies   then.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: This...  The picture   says vegetable oil.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Dip the cloth into the oil, then slowly rub all the shiny parts.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: I wonder what Vulcan will say when she sees how good   I did? Maybe I'll get a gift?
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: She made a top   for me last time. It's so fun to spin!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Maybe I'll get something even better this time.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Since it's food for my babies, it must taste good.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: (Ceobe dips her finger in the oil and licks it)
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Looks like I can't eat the food my babies like.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: And here I thought maybe we'd have something to enjoy together.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Oh, I have to wipe oil on other parts.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Grilled meatbeast chop! And mashed potatoes with sauce!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Vulcan is so good at crafting anything, even food!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Hm, what time is it now?
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Oh, eleven... eleven fifteen... It's noon!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: It's time for everyone to eat!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Wow, there's a lot of people here!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Let's see what food they have.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Hello, Ceobe. What do you want to eat?
attributes.name: Courier

attributes.content: (Since there's so much good food here, there must be more inside!)
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: (Okay, let me think how to sneak inside.)
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Courier, the food for your counter is almost here. Be ready.
attributes.name: Gitano

attributes.content: Vulcan taught me to watch closely and wait for a chance.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: I didn't watch enough last time and the old guy caught me at the door...
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: But this time will be different!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Shchi, huh? If I recall correctly, it goes there in the middle, where Courier is standing.
attributes.name: Gitano

attributes.content: (The door is close to my hiding spot.)
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: (There's a pretty lady by the door, I can't let her see me.)
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: (There's a lot of tasty stuff next to her, but people are watching.)
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: (There's a little hole further away. I think it is for dishes. I can't get through it.)
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Wooaahh! Kay, you can’t go in there!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: You can’t! Don’t you see the sign on the door?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I see a red circle with a tilty red line going through it.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: That means 'Kay is not allowed in here.' Got it?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: If you get it, why are you still going in?!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: If you’re hungry, you can just get in line and order something to eat.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Fine, fine! I’ll think of something!!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: If I give you this cookie, will you promise not to go inside?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Sorry Little Cub, I still want to go in.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Maybe I got found out because I was too excited.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: I won't make the same mistake again!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: (The only one by the door is the pretty lady at the counter.)
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Yummy yummy goodies, here I come!!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: What is it? Where are you going?
attributes.name: Gitano

attributes.content: (What do I do?! What do I do?!)
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: I-I want to go to the toilet.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: This isn't the toilet. There's a sign over there, look for the one with the blue and pink people.
attributes.name: Gitano

attributes.content: No problem, don't make the same mistake next time.
attributes.name: Gitano

attributes.content: (Ahh, I'm lucky she didn't figure me out. I don't want Vulcan to get mad at me.)
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Gitano, the last dish is here.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Ah, good job. This should go to the farthest corner where Noir Corne is.
attributes.name: Gitano

attributes.content: Ooh, I didn't know you two were THAT close.
attributes.name: Gitano

attributes.content: Don't joke about it, it hurts.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Put two standard meal sets at the prep station near the kitchen door.
attributes.name: Gitano

attributes.content: If you're joking, doesn't that mean I'm done for...
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Go on, we can wrap up and have lunch soon.
attributes.name: Gitano

attributes.content: There's no one there at all.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Even the pretty lady by the door is gone.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Ohh! There really was food here!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Ah, I'm so happy I got to eat!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: I better go home and finish taking care of my babies!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Just now, wasn't Little Cub's tummy rumbling?
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Is she hungry because she gave her cookie to me?
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Vulcan says that when people help you, you should pay it back double or triple or whatever's even more than those, I forgot! Fourple?
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Anyway, Little Cub gave me a small cookie, so I should give her a really really really——big cookie.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Okay, I'll make it as soon as Vulcan gets back!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Now I need to go home and finish up my work.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: The covers for the weapons and the bag are clean.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Vulcan, please hurry back, so Little Cub won't be hungry anymore...
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Ah, Vulcan! I'll get the door!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: You came back really early today.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Work went nice and smooth today, finished quick.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Can you let me see your maintenance work?
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: I just finished, the weapons are all neat on the table!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: (I did it just like the pictures  .)
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: The oil is applied very evenly.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: (Vulcan lifts the weapon and sniffs it)
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: I'm going back to the workshop. Do you want to come along?
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: This is a good batch of material here.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Hope I can make something satisfying out of it.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: (Go on, say it, say it! Little Cub is still starving!)
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: What's wrong? Is there anything you want to tell me?
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Can you teach me how to make a big cookie?!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Oh? You want to make your own food, finally?
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Please, teach me quickly! Little Cub is gonna starve to death soon!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Noon... Yeah, noon! I saw Little Cub at noon!
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: She gave me a really tasty cookie! So I want to give Little Cub an even bigger, even tastier one! But, I don't know how to make a cookie, and I don't know where Little Cub lives either, I-I——
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: You'll twist your tongue in a knot if you keep talking.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Sorry... I-I'm in a bit of a hurry...
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: I'll teach you how to make the treat, then bring you there.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: I'm always willing to teach if you're willing to learn.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: I happen to have some fermented dough here. Let's make a huge cookie, okay?
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: How big do you want it to be?
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Help me clear the workspace. I'll get the fire going.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Did you wash your hands, Kay?
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Just try it and see. I'll let you know if you're doing it wrong.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Don't be afraid to crush it, put some force into it.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Knead it for a few more minutes.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Alright, that should be enough. Spread it on the board.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Cut it in half with the knife.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Then press each half into a circle.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: We won't use any stuffing this time. I'll teach you how to prepare the stuffing and how to make pies when you're better at this.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: You missed a spot here, yes, here.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Take the dough on the board and put it into the oven.  Use these mitts for safety.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: On the rack in the oven?
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: What else do I need to do?
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: It's time to take the cookie out.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Just place it on the table and it's done.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: (Ceobe breaks off a piece and chews it)
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Cookies are best when they're still hot.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: I have to give this to Little Cub quickly.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: I'll put it between these wooden boards, so it'll stay warm longer.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: I'll guide you this time, but you have to go by yourself next time, got it?
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Come in, the door is open!
I ate your cookie earlier, so I got you a new one.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Vulcan taught me how to make it. It’s fresh outta the oven.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Hurry up and eat it before it gets cold.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: You don’t have to thank me.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Learn to do it well and you can make cookies by yourself next time.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Who knows, you might even be able to make your own honey biscuits one day.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: But I think I'd still eat your honey biscuits, Vulcan  !
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: Let's go back. We can't leave the fire alone for too long.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Besides, you haven't finished eating the other cookie yet.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: I was in such a rush to bring the cookie to Little Cub, I forgot my own.
attributes.name: Ceobe

attributes.content: That kind of cookie is fine for filling your stomach, but it still lacks a little something to make it really delicious.
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Do you remember the meat sauce from last time?
attributes.name: Vulcan

attributes.content: Want to dip your cookie in it?
attributes.name: Vulcan
